That means they have no faith in God.

01:24:25.840 --> 01:24:29.800
Shri Krishna has said, "Yogakshemam vahamyaham."

01:24:30.000 --> 01:24:31.760
When you will get your yoga

01:24:31.960 --> 01:24:33.160
when you'll get your union

01:24:33.360 --> 01:24:36.680
I'll look after your kshema, means your wellbeing.

