I could understand that we had to fight for our freedom.

01:24:52.760 --> 01:24:53.520
Tidak apa-apa.

01:24:53.720 --> 01:24:55.640
But after that fight

01:24:55.840 --> 01:24:58.760
now what do you have to have is yoga.

01:24:58.960 --> 01:25:01.280
First take to your yoga and He looks after you

01:25:01.480 --> 01:25:04.440
because this is the principle of wealth also

01:25:04.640 --> 01:25:07.880
of your wellbeing.

01:25:08.080 --> 01:25:10.080
Those who come to Sahaja Yoga

01:25:10.280 --> 01:25:12.960
somehow get their debts paid.

01:25:13.200 --> 01:25:16.120
They get out of all the financial entanglements.

01:25:16.320 --> 01:25:18.560
They get sufficient money to live well

01:25:18.760 --> 01:25:23.040
but not too much because that's an extreme.

01:25:23.240 --> 01:25:24.680
They live gloriously.

01:25:24.880 --> 01:25:27.600
They become generous people.

01:25:27.800 --> 01:25:31.720
Despite affluence I find people have no sense of generosity.

01:25:31.920 --> 01:25:32.880
They are saving money.

01:25:33.080 --> 01:25:35.240
Morning till evening saving so many pounds.

01:25:35.440 --> 01:25:36.960
Spend so much save so much.

01:25:37.160 --> 01:25:38.720
The advertisement goes like that.

01:25:38.920 --> 01:25:41.000
We spend so much and you save so much,

01:25:41.200 --> 01:25:43.520
and people are looking out for us how they can save money.

01:25:43.720 --> 01:25:46.240
Save for what?

01:25:46.440 --> 01:25:47.200
Untuk apa?

01:25:47.400 --> 01:25:50.440
To go to a pub?

01:25:50.640 --> 01:25:53.200
We have strikes, things like that.

01:25:53.400 --> 01:25:56.200
Australia is another one very much interested

01:25:56.400 --> 01:25:58.120
by this strikes business.

01:25:58.320 --> 01:26:00.040
We are suffering because of that.

01:26:00.240 --> 01:26:01.960
I can see that clearly.

01:26:02.160 --> 01:26:04.360
That's happening in England also same thing.

01:26:04.560 --> 01:26:05.520
The reason is

01:26:05.720 --> 01:26:07.600
you do not know why you want to save money

01:26:07.800 --> 01:26:09.160
why do you want to have more money.

01:26:09.360 --> 01:26:12.240
Is this bottomless pit

01:26:12.440 --> 01:26:17.560
which you have to fill with alcohol.

01:26:17.760 --> 01:26:21.920
Alcohol is the curse of the West.

01:26:22.120 --> 01:26:24.200
That is the curse of the West.

01:26:24.400 --> 01:26:26.160
But human nature is so funny

01:26:26.360 --> 01:26:28.640
that they see a man falling down on the ground

01:26:28.840 --> 01:26:30.560
and enter into the same pub

01:26:30.760 --> 01:26:32.560
to come back and fall on the other side.

01:26:32.760 --> 01:26:36.720
Perhaps they think the other side is missing so let's fill it up.

01:26:36.880 --> 01:26:38.760
It's so stupid to see.

01:26:38.960 --> 01:26:41.400
I mean I was living in a place near the church.

01:26:41.600 --> 01:26:45.080
to be the biggest church of England

01:26:45.280 --> 01:26:46.600
in Catholic Church

01:26:46.800 --> 01:26:52.320
and the only activity I saw there in the morning was

01:26:52.520 --> 01:26:53.640
itu

01:26:54.920 --> 01:26:58.720
beer. Big, big barrels of beer coming in

01:26:58.920 --> 01:27:01.000
and empty ones going out. Itu saja.

01:27:01.200 --> 01:27:03.280
No other entry no other exit.

01:27:03.480 --> 01:27:05.640
Only that much.

01:27:05.840 --> 01:27:08.080
From the back side from the sideways

01:27:08.280 --> 01:27:10.280
I saw this was the only thing going on

01:27:10.480 --> 01:27:15.280
and these priests are supposed to be godly people.

01:27:15.480 --> 01:27:17.680
It is so absurd you can't imagine.

01:27:17.880 --> 01:27:19.880
In Russia I went and they took me

01:27:20.080 --> 01:27:26.160
to a church. You see they had a Church of Orthodox.

01:27:26.360 --> 01:27:29.320
You too have here. I've seen Orthodox Church.

01:27:29.520 --> 01:27:32.080
And the fellow of the head of the church

01:27:32.280 --> 01:27:36.520
us that today that this is our fasting day so we can't eat meat

01:27:36.720 --> 01:27:38.400
but he drank so much

01:27:38.600 --> 01:27:40.800
that he become a drunk, you see.

01:27:41.000 --> 01:27:43.040
And we didn't know where to look.

01:27:43.240 --> 01:27:44.840
He got drunk completely.

01:27:45.040 --> 01:27:47.640
He was supposed to see us out because we are VIP's

01:27:47.840 --> 01:27:50.120
and there were three officers and then they started laughing.

01:27:50.320 --> 01:27:52.920
They said, "This is what Christianity is."

01:27:53.120 --> 01:27:54.600
I said "Why, why this?"

01:27:54.800 --> 01:27:56.120
He said, "You know what happend

01:27:56.320 --> 01:27:58.520
that Russians thought that they must also have a religion,

01:27:58.720 --> 01:28:00.640
after all everybody has a religion."

01:28:00.840 --> 01:28:02.680
They sent for someone.

01:28:02.880 --> 01:28:04.800
So the Muslims came in and they said,

01:28:05.000 --> 01:28:08.480
In Islam you can marry four times

01:28:08.680 --> 01:28:10.640
but you cannot have alcohol."

01:28:10.840 --> 01:28:12.720
They said, "This won't work out for such Russians.

01:28:12.920 --> 01:28:14.040
This is all right go out."

01:28:14.240 --> 01:28:16.640
So then they said, "Let's call Catholics."

01:28:16.800 --> 01:28:18.600
So they called Catholics

01:28:18.800 --> 01:28:23.280
and the Catholics said that, "You can

01:28:23.480 --> 01:28:26.720
have alcohol quite all right as much as you like."

01:28:26.920 --> 01:28:29.320
I don't know why they got this idea that they can have alcohol.

