01:28:52.240 --> 01:28:55.120
But Orthodox Church was like our gurus.

01:28:55.320 --> 01:28:56.920
Said, "Do what you like.

01:28:57.120 --> 01:29:00.680
We are not bothered as long as you give your purse to us."

01:29:00.880 --> 01:29:03.760
And that's how Orthodox Church came. Can you believe it?

01:29:03.960 --> 01:29:07.960
This is the plight of the churches, of the temples now.

