I asked a little boy who

01:29:10.280 --> 01:29:12.040
was taking drugs, a Western boy.

01:29:12.240 --> 01:29:13.360
I said, "From where do you get?"

01:29:13.560 --> 01:29:14.600
He said, "From the temples of India."

01:29:14.800 --> 01:29:17.160
Can you imagine the temples.

01:29:17.360 --> 01:29:20.480
While you people think that all that is Indian is great, you see.

01:29:20.680 --> 01:29:23.320
Temples are great.

01:29:23.520 --> 01:29:26.720
Even lamas are another institution by themselves.

01:29:26.920 --> 01:29:29.960
You think lamas are great people. We had a big

01:29:30.200 --> 01:29:31.640
argument on that.

01:29:31.840 --> 01:29:34.720
These lamas extracted blood out of that Tibet.

01:29:34.920 --> 01:29:35.840
You won't believe.

01:29:36.040 --> 01:29:38.600
If you see a Tibetan he's just

01:29:38.800 --> 01:29:41.840
any blood, without any flesh in him.

01:29:42.040 --> 01:29:44.520
And these people lived in big [GLASS?] place

01:29:44.720 --> 01:29:47.640
you see with the golden cups

01:29:47.840 --> 01:29:49.840
with golden plates.

01:29:50.040 --> 01:29:53.040
