01:29:53.240 --> 01:29:56.960
"If I come I must have a marble floor."

01:29:57.200 --> 01:30:00.160
What was he going to do with a marble floor? God only knows.

01:30:00.360 --> 01:30:01.920
Poor things. They starved themselves.

01:30:02.120 --> 01:30:04.040
These young people don't have so much money in the West.

01:30:04.240 --> 01:30:07.120
And made a marble floor for this great man to come in.

01:30:07.320 --> 01:30:09.640
He would sit seven feet high

01:30:09.840 --> 01:30:11.600
and what did he do there

01:30:11.800 --> 01:30:15.040
