01:30:56.800 --> 01:30:59.960
because it would be something like

01:31:00.200 --> 01:31:01.880
not arriving at a point

01:31:02.080 --> 01:31:04.240
nor completing what you are.

01:31:04.440 --> 01:31:08.040
You are not complete unless and until you become the Spirit.

01:31:08.240 --> 01:31:11.680
And this is the biggest problem today is to bring to people

01:31:11.880 --> 01:31:14.200
this simple fact. Sangat sederhana

01:31:14.400 --> 01:31:18.040
that Spirit is within you and can be enlightened

01:31:18.240 --> 01:31:20.040
spontaneously

01:31:20.240 --> 01:31:23.040
without any effort

01:31:23.240 --> 01:31:26.760
without reading about it because it's so [WHITE OR WIDE?].

01:31:26.960 --> 01:31:32.560
Just like your own heart beating.

