01:31:57.560 --> 01:31:59.680
This joy is boundless.

01:31:59.880 --> 01:32:01.960
Is your own.

01:32:02.200 --> 01:32:03.800
Is just waiting

01:32:03.960 --> 01:32:06.680
to open its door. The flood

01:32:06.880 --> 01:32:09.520
of that joy is going to come into your life.

