01:32:36.680 --> 01:32:40.360
he has given ten thousand people,

01:32:40.560 --> 01:32:42.840
and he's a miraculous man.

01:32:43.040 --> 01:32:46.440
It is very easy to mock at these things and to make fun of this.

01:32:46.640 --> 01:32:50.520
It's a sign of superficiality.

01:32:50.720 --> 01:32:52.120
Kamu hebat.

