Please don't open your eyes.

01:37:39.560 --> 01:37:42.280
Please just don't open your eyes

01:37:42.480 --> 01:37:43.880
because if you open your eyes

01:37:44.080 --> 01:37:46.400
kundalini won't rise above Agnya Chakra.

01:37:46.600 --> 01:37:49.160
So just keep your eyes shut.

01:37:49.360 --> 01:37:51.720
It will help a lot.

01:37:51.920 --> 01:37:53.680
Not to bend your neck too much

01:37:53.880 --> 01:37:56.680
to put back, but be straight.

01:37:56.880 --> 01:37:59.640
Be straight and parallel. Be comfortable.

01:37:59.840 --> 01:38:02.040
Put both the hands straight on the Mother Earth

01:38:02.240 --> 01:38:06.880
away from each other. Not touching each other.

01:38:27.040 --> 01:38:32.520
Now the first center that I told you about

01:38:32.720 --> 01:38:38.200
is the center of your chastity of your wisdom.

01:38:38.400 --> 01:38:42.320
So you have to say, "Mother please

01:38:42.520 --> 01:38:45.320
awaken the innocence within me."

01:38:45.520 --> 01:38:51.240
Just to say that because this is your right.

01:38:51.440 --> 01:38:54.480
cannot force you.

01:38:54.680 --> 01:38:57.600
You have to ask. This is your freedom.

01:38:57.800 --> 01:39:01.080
If you do not want it I cannot do it.

01:39:01.280 --> 01:39:08.720
You have to ask that, "Please awaken my innocence within me

01:39:08.920 --> 01:39:13.280
and my desire to be one

01:39:13.480 --> 01:39:19.560
with the Divine should be intense."

01:39:35.320 --> 01:39:38.840
"Please awaken my kundalini,

01:39:39.040 --> 01:39:43.320
this desire within me,

01:39:47.600 --> 01:39:55.880
and make me that all the technique of Divine love."

01:39:56.080 --> 01:40:00.920
That is called as shuddha vidya is the pure knowledge

01:40:01.120 --> 01:40:03.880
of the technique.

01:40:06.080 --> 01:40:10.600
You have to ask. That's the problem is

01:40:10.800 --> 01:40:14.320
because human beings have been given something

01:40:14.520 --> 01:40:17.640
which cannot be taken away.

01:40:22.560 --> 01:40:23.920
Not to feel guilty at all

01:40:24.120 --> 01:40:25.480
is again I said every time

01:40:25.680 --> 01:40:29.000
don't feel guilty.

01:40:29.200 --> 01:40:31.040
Don't say how can I do it. What will -

01:40:31.240 --> 01:40:32.800
It's all within you. It's just waiting.

01:40:33.000 --> 01:40:34.720
The whole instrument is there.

01:40:34.920 --> 01:40:38.280
Just I have to connect it. You just help me.

01:40:44.240 --> 01:40:45.960
By not feeling guilty at all

01:40:46.200 --> 01:40:49.280
because your guilt has no meaning at all

01:40:49.480 --> 01:40:53.320
to the ocean of love

01:40:53.520 --> 01:40:56.040
it's not even a speck. It can be washed off in no time

01:40:56.240 --> 01:40:59.840
so you just don't stick onto your guilt.

01:41:14.080 --> 01:41:18.720
Now left hand is your power of desire

01:41:18.920 --> 01:41:24.240
and right hand is your power of action.

01:41:24.440 --> 01:41:27.280
So keep the left hand as it is towards Me

01:41:27.480 --> 01:41:29.680
so the desire is steadied there

01:41:29.880 --> 01:41:35.960
and use the right hand first of all on your heart.

01:41:36.280 --> 01:41:39.720
Put your right hand on the heart.

01:41:39.920 --> 01:41:41.480
In the heart resides

01:41:41.680 --> 01:41:45.720
the Spirit, the reflection of God Almighty.

01:41:45.920 --> 01:41:51.520
So you have to say, "Mother make me the Spirit."

01:42:01.560 --> 01:42:04.280
Now you have to become the master.

01:42:04.480 --> 01:42:07.320
Master of all these trigunas,

01:42:07.520 --> 01:42:09.280
the three powers I've told you.

01:42:09.480 --> 01:42:11.320
Like you have got in a car

01:42:11.520 --> 01:42:13.320
the break and accelerator.

01:42:13.520 --> 01:42:16.120
You have these three powers within you

01:42:16.320 --> 01:42:18.600
by which

01:42:18.800 --> 01:42:21.680
you first of all you make mistakes these two powers

01:42:21.880 --> 01:42:24.160
and then you become the third power

01:42:24.360 --> 01:42:27.720
which is the automatic driving power.

01:42:27.920 --> 01:42:29.400
You learn it.

01:42:29.600 --> 01:42:34.800
Just becomes part and parcel of you. Don't think about it.

01:42:34.960 --> 01:42:39.640
And then the master is sitting behind the car.

01:42:39.840 --> 01:42:41.440
You become that.

01:42:41.640 --> 01:42:45.680
When you become the master you start seeing the driver in you

01:42:45.880 --> 01:42:47.880
you and all these powers within you

01:42:48.080 --> 01:42:49.880
and handle them

01:42:50.080 --> 01:42:53.800
just like a master handles his own vehicle

01:42:53.960 --> 01:42:57.040
you handle it and you just don't get into tantrums and

01:42:57.240 --> 01:43:00.040
you do all kinds of things which are not

01:43:00.240 --> 01:43:02.160
within your reach within your control.

01:43:02.360 --> 01:43:04.240
That's how you become the master.

01:43:04.440 --> 01:43:06.840
So to become the master you put your right hand

01:43:07.040 --> 01:43:09.880
your stomach on the left hand side.

01:43:10.080 --> 01:43:12.960
Right hand

01:43:13.160 --> 01:43:15.720
on the left hand side of your stomach.

01:43:15.920 --> 01:43:20.600
Right hand on the left hand side of your stomach.

01:43:20.800 --> 01:43:24.120
Right hand on the left hand side of your stomach

01:43:24.320 --> 01:43:28.040
left hand towards Me.

01:43:33.320 --> 01:43:40.960
Now you have to say, "Mother make me my own master."

01:43:41.160 --> 01:43:44.400
Say it thrice.

01:44:00.360 --> 01:44:02.480
Kemudian

01:44:02.680 --> 01:44:05.440
now you have to say, "Mother I am my own master."

01:44:05.640 --> 01:44:07.800
Put your left hand towards Me please.

01:44:07.960 --> 01:44:11.920
Left hand should be towards Me, yes.

01:44:12.120 --> 01:44:15.160
Open, open. Not closed hand.

01:44:15.360 --> 01:44:17.600
Now say, "Mother make me my own master."

01:44:17.800 --> 01:44:19.360
You have to be your own master.

01:44:19.560 --> 01:44:22.560
You are not to be guided by any master or anyone.

01:44:22.760 --> 01:44:26.600
It's your Spirit which is going to guide you.

01:44:39.640 --> 01:44:44.840
Just say ten times, "I am my own master."

01:45:14.000 --> 01:45:15.880
Now raise the same hand

01:45:16.080 --> 01:45:20.520
higher to the Spirit to your heart

01:45:20.720 --> 01:45:26.440
and now say 10 times, "Mother I am the Spirit."

01:45:29.440 --> 01:45:30.360
Ten times.

01:45:30.560 --> 01:45:33.520
Just right hand. Don't move left hand. Only move right hand.

01:45:33.720 --> 01:45:36.120
Left hand you keep all the time stretched.

01:45:36.320 --> 01:45:39.160
hand you move to the heart and say ten times,

01:45:39.360 --> 01:45:44.040
"Mother I am the Spirit."

01:45:53.480 --> 01:45:55.760
Sekarang.

01:46:07.640 --> 01:46:11.560
Put the right hand on the left hand side of your neck.

01:46:11.760 --> 01:46:15.040
Left hand side of your neck on the Vishuddhi Chakra.

01:46:15.240 --> 01:46:16.320
The Left Vishuddhi.

01:46:16.520 --> 01:46:20.840
We are working on the left throughout.

01:46:21.040 --> 01:46:24.400
So you say, "Mother

01:46:24.600 --> 01:46:26.120
I am not guilty."

01:46:26.320 --> 01:46:31.960
sixteen times as a punishment.

01:46:49.800 --> 01:46:54.520
Just say, "Mother I am not guilty."

01:47:02.720 --> 01:47:06.760
Sixteen times.

01:47:09.160 --> 01:47:11.360
This will cure lots of your problems

01:47:11.560 --> 01:47:15.800
of guilt, of diffidence.

01:47:22.840 --> 01:47:25.760
You cannot be guilty because you are the Spirit.

01:47:25.960 --> 01:47:28.000
The Spirit cannot be guilty.

01:47:36.440 --> 01:47:37.920
Now put your right hand again.

01:47:38.120 --> 01:47:42.920
Left hand being there where it is. On your forehead across.

01:47:43.120 --> 01:47:46.520
On your forehead across

01:47:46.720 --> 01:47:49.920
at the center of our Lord Jesus Christ

01:47:50.120 --> 01:47:55.560
and say, "Mother I forgive everyone."

01:47:55.760 --> 01:48:01.720
With your full heart you should say, "Mother I forgive everyone."

01:48:09.960 --> 01:48:13.760
Because if you don't forgive you are working under a myth

01:48:13.960 --> 01:48:16.520
because you are not troubling the person.

01:48:16.720 --> 01:48:18.800
The person is troubling you.

01:48:19.000 --> 01:48:23.200
Just say, "Mother I forgive everyone."

01:48:23.400 --> 01:48:26.040
Some people say it is difficult. It is the easiest thing.

01:48:26.240 --> 01:48:32.160
Just your mental projection it is.

01:48:55.640 --> 01:48:59.040
Now put this right hand on top of your head.

01:48:59.240 --> 01:49:01.160
You'll find it's little hot.

01:49:01.400 --> 01:49:02.800
The heat is coming out of your body.

01:49:02.960 --> 01:49:07.320
Just put it on top of your head. Kepala.

01:49:07.680 --> 01:49:09.840
The heat is coming out. Press it.

01:49:10.040 --> 01:49:13.320
The palm of the hand should be pressed in the center.

01:49:13.520 --> 01:49:18.320
find there is a heat. Press it.

01:49:18.760 --> 01:49:22.360
At this point you have to have to ask for your realization again

01:49:22.560 --> 01:49:24.320
because I cannot force it on you.

01:49:24.520 --> 01:49:26.960
So you have to say, "Mother I want my realization.

01:49:27.200 --> 01:49:31.040
Please give me my realization.

01:49:37.280 --> 01:49:38.840
I'm a seeker of truth.

01:49:39.040 --> 01:49:44.160
Please give me my realization, Mother."

01:49:55.600 --> 01:50:01.640
Now raise your hand and see if there is a cool breeze coming out.

01:50:11.640 --> 01:50:14.320
You can change your hand. Put your right hand towards Me

01:50:14.520 --> 01:50:18.400
and put the left hand and see if there's a cool breeze coming out.

01:50:18.600 --> 01:50:24.640
Right hand towards Me not closed but open, open hand.

01:50:28.200 --> 01:50:30.560
[FIRST TIME?]

01:50:30.760 --> 01:50:32.960
which is doing all the living work,

01:50:33.200 --> 01:50:36.640
everything around us.

01:50:38.280 --> 01:50:41.600
Now put down your hands please

01:50:41.800 --> 01:50:45.720
and see if you are feeling now in your hands.

01:50:45.920 --> 01:50:50.480
Just see if you are feeling in your hands also.

01:50:50.680 --> 01:50:52.720
feel very relaxed.

01:50:52.920 --> 01:50:57.240
[COULD BRING?] peace, bliss of God

01:50:57.440 --> 01:51:02.720
and kingdom of God on this Earth.

01:51:10.360 --> 01:51:15.800
Please raise the hands who have felt the cool breeze in their hands

01:51:20.720 --> 01:51:23.000
All of you have felt it.

01:51:23.200 --> 01:51:25.240
Itu keren.

01:51:25.440 --> 01:51:28.600
Very great.

01:51:28.800 --> 01:51:30.800
So many of you have felt.

01:51:30.960 --> 01:51:34.640
May God bless you.

01:51:34.840 --> 01:51:37.880
You need not think about it.

01:51:38.080 --> 01:51:44.640
Only thing I will tell you how to fix your kundalini better

01:51:44.840 --> 01:51:48.040
because you see it's like fixing

01:51:48.240 --> 01:51:52.200
it into a plug properly otherwise it can be loose a little bit.

01:51:52.400 --> 01:51:58.160
So Warren will tell you how to do it. Just tell.

01:51:58.360 --> 01:52:00.760
WARREN: Just put your left hand near the kundalini at this point.

01:52:00.960 --> 01:52:02.360
SHRI MATAJI: Put the left hand

01:52:02.560 --> 01:52:05.680
towards your kundalini, little in front.

01:52:05.880 --> 01:52:08.360
WARREN: And the right hand in front

01:52:08.560 --> 01:52:11.960
and you come around in that fashion.

01:52:12.160 --> 01:52:19.160
SHRI MATAJI: First higher, forward, lower, backwards.

01:52:19.360 --> 01:52:20.360
Like that.

01:52:20.560 --> 01:52:22.720
You have to move. This is the left hand which moves steady

01:52:22.920 --> 01:52:26.120
and the right hand moves round and round like that clockwise.

01:52:26.320 --> 01:52:27.560
Now you go on moving it.

01:52:27.760 --> 01:52:28.640
WARREN: You raise it.

01:52:28.840 --> 01:52:31.200
SHRI MATAJI: Raise it - your kundalini. Go up.

01:52:31.400 --> 01:52:33.920
Take it up. Push back your hands.

01:52:34.120 --> 01:52:35.560
them loose.

01:52:35.760 --> 01:52:39.080
Push it up. [MAKE IT A BIT?]. Twist

01:52:39.280 --> 01:52:41.800
on top of your head

01:52:42.000 --> 01:52:45.360
and now give it a knot.

01:52:45.560 --> 01:52:48.760
This is first time. This is for the first power.

01:52:48.960 --> 01:52:50.920
For the second power again

01:52:51.120 --> 01:52:55.680
put your hand in front of your kundalini but do it properly.

01:52:55.880 --> 01:53:00.800
Higher, in front, lower and backwards again.

01:53:01.000 --> 01:53:04.800
Start doing it. Raise it.

01:53:07.760 --> 01:53:08.800
Go high

01:53:08.960 --> 01:53:11.680
and push your back your hands

01:53:11.880 --> 01:53:15.520
and just give it a big twist again.

01:53:15.720 --> 01:53:19.360
Now for third power you have to do it thrice. Three knots.

01:53:19.560 --> 01:53:22.120
Don't put down your hands but just do it three times.

01:53:22.320 --> 01:53:23.440
Again let's do it.

01:53:23.640 --> 01:53:27.880
are raising your own kundalini.

01:53:29.720 --> 01:53:32.920
Go up again. Push back your hands. Give fast twist.

01:53:33.120 --> 01:53:35.480
Keep your hands there. Give it a knot.

01:53:35.680 --> 01:53:38.760
Again twist your hand

01:53:38.960 --> 01:53:41.080
and give it a knot.

01:53:41.280 --> 01:53:43.600
Again twist your hand

01:53:43.800 --> 01:53:45.840
and now give it a big knot.

01:53:46.040 --> 01:53:52.120
Now see for yourself if your hands are working better.

01:53:58.320 --> 01:54:01.440
These are the hands that are going to speak

01:54:01.640 --> 01:54:03.920
as told by Muhammad Sahab

01:54:04.120 --> 01:54:08.520
that at the time of your resurrection your hands will speak.

01:54:08.720 --> 01:54:12.320
Now you can see that in the hands he has shown the chakras,

01:54:12.520 --> 01:54:14.040
the fingertips.

01:54:14.240 --> 01:54:15.840
All these I will tell you.

01:54:16.040 --> 01:54:18.320
Today's three chakras I'll tell you where they are.

01:54:18.520 --> 01:54:21.400
Left side is left side. Right side is right side

01:54:21.600 --> 01:54:23.640
and the center side is here.

01:54:23.840 --> 01:54:25.760
And the three chakras we have.

01:54:25.960 --> 01:54:28.320
The first chakras is this one on the left hand side.

01:54:28.520 --> 01:54:30.240
This is right hand side first chakra.

01:54:30.440 --> 01:54:32.720
And the second chakra we have are these.

01:54:32.920 --> 01:54:35.440
One on the left hand side, right hand side.

01:54:35.640 --> 01:54:39.480
And the third chakra are these.

01:54:39.680 --> 01:54:41.920
Both the left hand side and right hand side.

01:54:42.120 --> 01:54:43.320
Now what you feel

01:54:43.520 --> 01:54:46.000
if there's something wrong with these chakras within yourself

01:54:46.200 --> 01:54:48.440
you will feel a little burning

01:54:48.640 --> 01:54:51.880
or maybe little numbness

01:54:52.080 --> 01:54:53.680
maybe some heaviness.

01:54:53.880 --> 01:54:57.760
What all these things indicate I'll tell you tomorrow.

01:54:57.960 --> 01:54:59.720
And on other people also you can feel

01:54:59.920 --> 01:55:01.880
but just now you don't try with other people

01:55:02.080 --> 01:55:05.640
because it's like a sprouting of a seed which is very delicate.

01:55:05.840 --> 01:55:07.480
You have to look after it.

01:55:07.680 --> 01:55:10.360
Tomorrow and day after we'll work it out.

01:55:10.560 --> 01:55:13.280
You establish yourself fully in Sahaja Yoga.

01:55:13.480 --> 01:55:18.440
You have to become a guru, a complete guru of your own.

01:55:18.640 --> 01:55:21.880
May God bless you.

01:55:34.080 --> 01:55:38.680
WARREN: As Mother said there will be a workshop on Sunday.

01:55:38.880 --> 01:55:43.160
We'll give the address tomorrow night, Friday night

01:55:43.360 --> 01:55:44.360
SHRI MATAJI: You tell them just now.

01:55:44.560 --> 01:55:46.880
WARREN: and you are all invited.

01:55:47.080 --> 01:55:49.400
Mother will work it out.

01:55:49.600 --> 01:55:51.640
Dan

01:55:51.880 --> 01:55:55.440
the whole day free because we're happy to show you

01:55:55.640 --> 01:55:58.280
all the aspects of Kundalini and the chakras.

01:55:58.480 --> 01:56:01.640
Bring your lunch along.

01:56:01.840 --> 01:56:03.480
It should be a good day.

01:56:03.680 --> 01:56:07.080
Tomorrow evening Mother will speak about the Heart Chakra,

01:56:07.280 --> 01:56:09.960
the center of security within us.

01:56:10.200 --> 01:56:12.320
The Vishuddhi Chakra which is the center

01:56:12.520 --> 01:56:15.760
in which we are able to witness the drama of life

01:56:15.960 --> 01:56:17.760
and get our self esteem.

01:56:17.960 --> 01:56:22.200
And the Agnya Chakra which is the center of Christ which relates to

01:56:22.400 --> 01:56:24.520
the principle of the Spirit,

01:56:24.720 --> 01:56:26.800
the quality of forgiveness.

01:56:26.960 --> 01:56:31.160
And then finally the Sahasrara Chakra which is the center

01:56:31.360 --> 01:56:36.120
which Mataji Herself has opened in this incarnation.

01:56:36.320 --> 01:56:41.640
So the two successive lectures are going to deal with those centers.

01:56:41.800 --> 01:56:44.360
Thank you very much and good evening.
